{"Id":635627,"Title":"贞节祠","Dynasty":"明","Author":"黎暹","Context":"夫妇君臣，人之大伦。妇之从夫，犹臣于君。一有急难，均为死节。庶几大义，不愧臣妾。卓卓贤周，义不忘刘。濒危绐贼，窜身中流。中流陨命，不但已已。容服整然，死如不死。七日浮尸，溯流而还。夫故身同，面夫昔颜。以义捐躯，孰不震骇。坟祠像设，孰忍迁改。几经兵燹，忽焉就荒。有贤诸孙，嘅念弗忘。既修其祠，复饰其像。澜海之壖，桂圃之上。纂志标题，经两翰林。我言奚似，纪还于今。薄俗何人，逆臣悖妇。闻风革心，凛然千古。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"dee67b4527f5ee839b679794b0e8b508","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":7284654,"Sentence":"澜海之壖，桂圃之上。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lán hǎi zhī 壖，guì pǔ zhī shǎng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":15,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284655,"Sentence":"纂志标题，经两翰林。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zuǎn zhì biāo tǐ ，jīng liǎng hàn lǐn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":16,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284656,"Sentence":"我言奚似，纪还于今。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ yán xī shì ，ji hái yú jīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":17,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284657,"Sentence":"薄俗何人，逆臣悖妇。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"báo sú hé rén ，nì chén bèi fù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":18,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284658,"Sentence":"闻风革心，凛然千古。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wén fēng gé xīn ，lin rán qiān gǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":19,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284639,"Sentence":"夫妇君臣，人之大伦。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fū fù jūn chén ，rén zhī dà lún ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284640,"Sentence":"妇之从夫，犹臣于君。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fù zhī cóng fū ，yóu chén yú jūn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284641,"Sentence":"一有急难，均为死节。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yī yǒu jǐ nán ，jūn wéi si jiē ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7284642,"Sentence":"庶几大义，不愧臣妾。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shù jī dà yǐ ，bú kuì chén qiè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":